channel.title: Need help with running my 508 server
channel.description:
Hey guys, I'm trying to figure this whole thing out with 508 servers, and I'm running into nothing but problems.
My ip changer keeps on freezing up on "connecting to update server," I have my cache in the right place, my server is running, and I have tried downloading new ip changers. Under the cmd window it says, "error_game_js5io." Reading other topics, people have said that this is caused by not renaming your cache "cache508," and by not placing your downloaded cache in it; however, looking at many guides I have correctly placed my cache, and still the same problem persists.
Please help me, I don't know what I'm doing wrong.
